actionName: Check for loose/damage connection from DIO280 to PLC relay 58K3 coil supply. Replace the wire if found faulty.
infoName:
Missing nacelle fan feedback signal. When *DO_NacelleFan* is high *DI_FB_NacelleFan* is expected to be high and vice versa.
Troubleshooting guide built on the basis of below mention drawing version and software version.
Bottom Cabinet Drawing Version: E.05.1.1.2.101A Rev.001.
Top Cabinet Drawing Version: E.05.1.2.2.101A Rev.000.
Hub Cabinet Drawing Version: E.05.1.3.2.101A Rev.001_Improved.
Software Version: CSM6321X5SX1XXR007.
